Title: Corioliss City Style Pink Tourmaline Ceramic Hair Straightener
Description: Apt for the peppy and vivacious women of today is this Corioliss City Style Pink Tourmaline Ceramic Hair Straightener. This straightener comes with multiple features which help you make your hair smooth and sleek without much hassle. Tourmaline Ceramic Plates As this straightener comes with tourmaline ceramic plates, you are left with smooth and soft hair at the end of the straightening process. These plates further help retain the moisture in your hair by sealing the cuticle layer. Adding to this, the plates help the straightener glide through your hair with much ease. Far Infrared Technology The far infrared technology of this straightener allow the heat to penetrate into your hair and make it straight and smooth. This technology also ensures that the heat doesn’t damage your hair during the straightening process. Anti-Static Preventing your hair from becoming frizzy and dry is the anti-static feature of this straightener. The anti-static feature helps eliminate the static electricity in your hair. LED indicator Allowing you to see when the straightener is on and ready for use is the LED indicator of this straightener. On / Off Switch Facilitating easy operation of the straightener is the on and off switch it is equipped with. Fast Heater Element Ensuring that you won’t have to wait for too long to use the straightener on your hair is the fast heater element it comes with. This element also acts as a thermostat and doesn't let the straightener get overheated.  Variable Temperature Control As this straightener comes with a variable temperature control, you can choose the heat which best suits your hair type and the hairdo you want. For thin hair a low temperature, whereas for thick hair a high temperature would be appropriate. 210° Maximum Temperature Leaving you with salon-like hair is the maximum temperature of 210° this straightener offers. This allows you to style and straighten your hair perfectly. 360° Swivel Cord  Equipped with a 360° swivel cord, the wire of this straightener doesn’t get tangled or twisted while you are straightening your hair.
